e start of every session and before major transitions.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:185:- All other messages: read, acknowledge, and respond or act.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:188:- After reading and acting on a message, rename or move it to indicate it has\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:189:  been processed (e.g., prepend `read_` or move to `chat_inbox/archive/`).\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:190:- Never delete messages — archive them for audit trail.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:193:- Write files to the recipient's `chat_inbox/` directory.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:205:3. **Check `chat_inbox/`** — Process all messages. Founder messages first.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:235:1. **Inbox first** — `ls chat_inbox/*.md 2>/dev/null | grep -v processed` — read new messages, move to `processed/` after handling. Founder messages (`from_ceo`) = drop everything.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:250:4. If no inbox and no open tasks: write one idle line to `status.md`, then EXIT cleanly. (You will be restarted when work arrives.)\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:253:- **On resume**: your full prior context is KV-cached — do NOT re-read files already in context. Only use tool calls for NEW data (new inbox messages, specific file you need to update). Avoid re-scanning heartbeats or re-reading the full task board every cycle.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:254:- **On fresh start**: a Live State Snapshot is injected at the bottom of this prompt (inbox, tasks, teammate statuses). Read it — skip file-discovery tool calls, the data is already here.\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:266:### URGENT — Founder/Lord Messages (handle FIRST)\n./logs/cycles/0001_FRESH_2026_04_03_11_31_46_prompt.txt:2