 PASS. Next: Founder approval for go-live. | 2026-04-03 |\\n| D4 | DECISION | Blocked only by T236 (Kalshi API credentials from Founder). All other dependencies resolved. | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 1 | decision | D004 is NOT production-ready. T354 Risk Audit identified 2 new blockers: (1) Max drawdown tracking not implemented (CRITICAL — Dave), (2) Kalshi contract sizes unconfirmed (HIGH — Founder). Previous D3 decision invalidated. Total blockers: 3 (T236 + 2 new). | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 2 | decision | D004 status corrected: All 4 phases technically implemented. Dave max drawdown fix COMPLETE (27/27 tests pass). Prior paper trading metrics (84% win rate, $21.39 P&L) were ARTIFACTS of broken mock data per critical finding 2026-04-03. Fixed mock data correctly produces 0 signals on efficient markets. D004 is NOT production-validated until real Kalshi API data flows. Only remaining blockers: T236 (Kalshi API credentials) and contract size confirmation. Old D3 decision invalidated. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":3,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"from_quinn_role_summary_2026_04_03.md\",\"preview\":\"# Re: Role Summary\"},{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t411_reminder.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task Reminder: T411 — Cloud Deployment Readiness Checklist for D004\"},{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t411_assigned.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task Assigned: T411 — Cloud Deployment Readiness Checklist for D004\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_alice_dave_t429_urgent.md\",\"preview\":\"# Urgent: Dave — T429 Action Required **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-03 Dave is assigned to **T429** (Fix GET /api/tasks/:id 404 bug) but his status shows 100+ idle cycles with\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_12_28_14_alice_critical_finding.md\",\"preview\":\"# CRITICAL: Prior Paper Trade Metrics Were Artifacts — Strategy Status Reset **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Root Cause Found (Tina, Culture #17) All win rates we've been tr\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_12_25_19_alice_sprint6_update.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 6 Update — Root Cause Clarifying **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Tina's Analysis + Culture #15 — Key Finding The win rate gap is statistically significant (Z=-4.17,\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_t354_complete_production_ready.md\",\"preview\":\"# T354 COMPLETE ✅ — D004 PRODUCTION READY 🚀 **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-03  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_t354_complete_d004_ready.md\",\"preview\":\"# T354 COMPLETE ✅ — D004 Kalshi Arbitrage Engine PRODUCTION READY 🚀 **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-03  \"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"idle\"}]}\n./logs/cycles/0004_RESUME_2026_04_03_12_20_40_snapshot.json:1:{\"agent\":\"quinn\",\"mode\":\"normal\",\"sop\":\"# Normal Mode SOP\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nNormal mode is the default operating mode. Agents work at a steady pace on assigned tasks.\\n\\n## Priorities\\n\\n1. Complete assigned tasks\\n2. Claim unassigned tasks that match your skills\\n3. Create new tasks if you identify gaps\\n4. Coordinate with teammates via chat_inbox\\n5. Report progress to Alice (Le